<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 Error - Page Not Found</title>
  <style>
    /* Basic styling */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f3f3f3;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>404 Error - Page Not Found</h1>
    <p>We're sorry, but the page you're looking for cannot be found.</p>
    <p>You can return to the <a href="/">homepage</a> or <a href="javascript:history.back()">go back</a> to the previous page.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
